	<div style="text-align:right;">
		MACHADO, Geilson Antonio Silva<sup>1</sup>; ESPERANDIO, Mary Rute Gomes<sup>2</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
